---
import Head from '../../components/Head.astro';
import '../../styles/fonts.css';
---

<html lang="fr">
	<head>
		<Head
			title="Pascale Richard — Ensemble pour NY 2026"
			description="Candidate Renaissance pour les Français de New York, New Jersey et Connecticut. Journaliste, élue, engagée depuis 2016."
			path="/v/2"
		/>
	</head>
	<body>
		<!-- ═══ SLIDE 1 — HERO (dark navy) ═══ -->
		<section class="slide slide-hero">
			<nav>
				<img src="/assets/logos/RENAISSANCE_logo-complet_blanc.png" alt="Renaissance" class="nav-logo" />
			</nav>

			<div class="hero-inner">
				<div class="portrait-wrapper">
					<img src="/assets/images/pascale.jpg" alt="Pascale Richard" class="portrait" />
				</div>
				<h1 class="fade-in">Pascale Richard</h1>
				<p class="role fade-in delay-1">Conseillère des Français de l'étranger</p>
				<div class="geo fade-in delay-1">
					<span>New York</span>
					<span class="dot"></span>
					<span>New Jersey</span>
					<span class="dot"></span>
					<span>Connecticut</span>
				</div>

				<div class="divider fade-in delay-2"></div>

				<p class="quote fade-in delay-2">« Le plus satisfaisant est d'aider mes concitoyens. Conseiller des Français de l'étranger est une fonction méconnue, mais les conseillers font un travail important. »</p>

				<ul class="facts fade-in delay-3">
					<li><strong>25+ ans</strong> à New York</li>
					<li><strong>Engagée</strong> depuis 2016</li>
					<li><strong>Élue</strong> en 2021</li>
					<li><strong>Suppléante</strong> de R. Lescure</li>
				</ul>

				<div class="buttons fade-in delay-3">
					<a href="https://www.instagram.com/pascalevrichard" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="cta">Suivez-nous sur Instagram</a>
					<a href="https://renaissance-fde.fr/portrait-dune-elue-a-votre-service-pascale-richard-new-york/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="cta ghost">Découvrir Pascale</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ═══ SLIDE 2 — PRIORITIES (white) ═══ -->
		<section class="slide slide-priorities">
			<div class="container">
				<p class="section-label">Engagements</p>
				<h2>Trois priorités pour notre communauté</h2>
				<div class="priority-grid">
					<div class="priority-card">
						<div class="card-accent"></div>
						<div class="card-number">01</div>
						<h3>Solidarité</h3>
						<p>Accompagner les Français en difficulté aux États-Unis — personnes âgées isolées, malades, familles touchées par la vie chère. Orienter chacun vers les bons interlocuteurs.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="priority-card">
						<div class="card-accent"></div>
						<div class="card-number">02</div>
						<h3>Lien &amp; événements</h3>
						<p>Soutenir les associations et événements qui créent du lien — de Bastille Day aux salons de l'éducation bilingue — et rassembler les Français de toute la circonscription.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="priority-card">
						<div class="card-accent"></div>
						<div class="card-number">03</div>
						<h3>Services numériques</h3>
						<p>Accompagner la mise en place de France Consulaire et le vote par Internet. Tenir les Français informés, simplifier les démarches administratives à distance.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ═══ SLIDE 3 — QUOTE BAND (blue) ═══ -->
		<section class="slide slide-quote">
			<div class="container">
				<blockquote>
					« Il y a une résilience des gens qui n'attendent pas tout de leur gouvernement. C'est notre relation à l'État qui doit évoluer. »
				</blockquote>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ═══ SLIDE 4 — TIMELINE (light) ═══ -->
		<section class="slide slide-parcours">
			<div class="container narrow">
				<p class="section-label">Parcours</p>
				<h2>D'une carrière dans les médias à l'engagement politique</h2>
				<div class="timeline">
					<div class="tl-item">
						<span class="tl-year">Années 2000</span>
						<div class="tl-content">
							<h4>Installation à New York</h4>
							<p>Carrière de journaliste. Rédactrice en chef de France Amérique. Directrice des événements culturels au Lycée Français de New York.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="tl-item">
						<span class="tl-year">2016</span>
						<div class="tl-content">
							<h4>Engagement avec En Marche</h4>
							<p>S'engage dès la première heure avec le mouvement d'Emmanuel Macron. Campagne aux côtés de Roland Lescure pour l'Amérique du Nord.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="tl-item">
						<span class="tl-year">2017</span>
						<div class="tl-content">
							<h4>Suppléante du député Lescure</h4>
							<p>Suppléante pendant la première mandature du député de la 1ère circonscription des Français établis hors de France.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="tl-item">
						<span class="tl-year">2021</span>
						<div class="tl-content">
							<h4>Élue conseillère des Français de l'étranger</h4>
							<p>Tête de liste En Marche pour NY, NJ, CT et les Bermudes. Élue à l'Assemblée des Français de l'étranger, commission développement durable.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="tl-item current">
						<span class="tl-year">2026</span>
						<div class="tl-content">
							<h4>Candidate aux législatives</h4>
							<p>Candidate Renaissance aux élections législatives pour représenter les Français de la circonscription tri-state.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ═══ SLIDE 5 — EVENTS (white) ═══ -->
		<section class="slide slide-events">
			<div class="container">
				<p class="section-label">Événements</p>
				<h2>Rencontrons-nous</h2>
				<div class="events-placeholder">
					<p class="coming-soon">À venir</p>
					<p class="events-sub">Le calendrier des événements et rencontres sera bientôt disponible. Suivez-nous sur Instagram pour rester informé.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ═══ SLIDE 6 — CTA + FOOTER (dark navy) ═══ -->
		<section class="slide slide-final">
			<div class="final-inner">
				<div class="cta-block">
					<h2>Rejoignez le mouvement</h2>
					<p class="cta-sub">Ensemble, construisons l'avenir de notre communauté française aux États-Unis.</p>
					<div class="buttons">
						<a href="https://www.instagram.com/pascalevrichard" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="cta">Suivez-nous sur Instagram</a>
						<a href="https://renaissance-fde.fr/portrait-dune-elue-a-votre-service-pascale-richard-new-york/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="cta ghost-light">Découvrir Pascale</a>
					</div>
				</div>
				<footer>
					<img src="/assets/logos/RENAISSANCE_monogramme_marine.png" alt="Renaissance" class="footer-logo" />
					<p>&copy; 2026 Pascale Richard &mdash; Ensemble pour NY 2026</p>
				</footer>
			</div>
		</section>
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	/* ─── VARIABLES ─── */
	:root {
		--navy: #001B6E;
		--blue: #002395;
		--red: #ED2939;
		--white: #FFFFFF;
		--gold: #C9A84C;
		--text: #1A1A2E;
		--light: #F7F7FB;
		--border: #E4E4EC;
	}

	/* ─── RESET ─── */
	* { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

	/* ─── SCROLL SNAP SETUP ─── */
	html {
		font-family: 'Maax', system-ui, sans-serif;
		color: var(--text);
		font-size: 16px;
		scroll-snap-type: y mandatory;
		overflow-y: scroll;
		scroll-behavior: smooth;
	}

	body {
		overflow-x: hidden;
	}

	/* ─── GENERIC SLIDE ─── */
	.slide {
		height: 100vh;
		scroll-snap-align: start;
		overflow: hidden;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		justify-content: center;
		align-items: center;
		position: relative;
	}

	.container {
		max-width: 1000px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 0 2rem;
		width: 100%;
	}

	.container.narrow {
		max-width: 720px;
	}

	/* ─── FADE IN ANIMATION ─── */
	@keyframes fadeInUp {
		from {
			opacity: 0;
			transform: translateY(24px);
		}
		to {
			opacity: 1;
			transform: translateY(0);
		}
	}

	.fade-in {
		animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out both;
	}

	.delay-1 { animation-delay: 0.15s; }
	.delay-2 { animation-delay: 0.3s; }
	.delay-3 { animation-delay: 0.5s; }

	/* ─── NAV (pinned top-left) ─── */
	nav {
		position: fixed;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
		z-index: 100;
	}

	.nav-logo {
		height: 20px;
		opacity: 0.8;
	}

	/* ═══════════════════════════════════════
	   SLIDE 1 — HERO (dark navy)
	   ═══════════════════════════════════════ */
	.slide-hero {
		background: var(--navy);
		color: var(--white);
		text-align: center;
	}

	.hero-inner {
		max-width: 640px;
		padding: 0 2rem;
	}

	.portrait-wrapper {
		margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
	}

	.portrait {
		width: 140px;
		height: 140px;
		border-radius: 50%;
		object-fit: cover;
		object-position: center top;
		border: 3px solid var(--gold);
		box-shadow: 0 0 60px rgba(201, 168, 76, 0.2);
	}

	.slide-hero h1 {
		font-size: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 6rem);
		font-weight: 700;
		line-height: 1.02;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		color: var(--white);
		letter-spacing: -0.02em;
	}

	.role {
		font-size: 1.125rem;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65);
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	.geo {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.75rem;
		font-size: 0.8125rem;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.12em;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.dot {
		width: 4px;
		height: 4px;
		border-radius: 50%;
		background: var(--gold);
	}

	.divider {
		width: 50px;
		height: 3px;
		background: var(--gold);
		margin: 0 auto 1.75rem;
		border-radius: 2px;
	}

	.slide-hero .quote {
		font-size: 1.0625rem;
		font-style: italic;
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		max-width: 480px;
		margin-left: auto;
		margin-right: auto;
	}

	.facts {
		list-style: none;
		display: flex;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		gap: 0.375rem 1.25rem;
		justify-content: center;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}

	.facts li {
		font-size: 0.8125rem;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45);
	}

	.facts strong {
		color: var(--gold);
	}

	.slide-hero .buttons {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1rem;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	/* ─── BUTTONS (shared) ─── */
	.cta {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 0.875rem 2.25rem;
		border-radius: 4px;
		font-weight: 700;
		font-size: 1rem;
		text-decoration: none;
		transition: all 0.2s;
		background: var(--red);
		color: var(--white);
	}

	.cta:hover { background: #c4212f; }

	.cta.ghost {
		background: transparent;
		color: var(--white);
		border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
	}

	.cta.ghost:hover {
		border-color: var(--white);
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
	}

	.cta.ghost-light {
		background: transparent;
		color: var(--white);
		border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.35);
	}

	.cta.ghost-light:hover {
		border-color: var(--white);
		background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
	}

	/* ═══════════════════════════════════════
	   SLIDE 2 — PRIORITIES (white)
	   ═══════════════════════════════════════ */
	.slide-priorities {
		background: var(--white);
	}

	.section-label {
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.15em;
		font-size: 0.8125rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: var(--red);
		margin-bottom: 0.625rem;
		text-align: center;
	}

	.slide-priorities h2 {
		text-align: center;
		font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.75rem);
		color: var(--blue);
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
		line-height: 1.2;
	}

	.priority-grid {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
		gap: 1.75rem;
	}

	.priority-card {
		position: relative;
		background: var(--light);
		padding: 2.25rem 1.75rem;
		border-radius: 10px;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.card-accent {
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		width: 100%;
		height: 3px;
		background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--blue), var(--red));
	}

	.card-number {
		font-size: 0.8125rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: var(--red);
		margin-bottom: 0.875rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.05em;
	}

	.priority-card h3 {
		font-size: 1.1875rem;
		color: var(--blue);
		margin-bottom: 0.625rem;
	}

	.priority-card p {
		font-size: 0.9375rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: #555;
	}

	/* ═══════════════════════════════════════
	   SLIDE 3 — QUOTE BAND (blue)
	   ═══════════════════════════════════════ */
	.slide-quote {
		background: var(--blue);
	}

	.slide-quote blockquote {
		max-width: 700px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 3vw, 2rem);
		font-style: italic;
		line-height: 1.6;
		color: var(--white);
		text-align: center;
		position: relative;
		padding: 0 2rem;
	}

	.slide-quote blockquote::before {
		content: '';
		display: block;
		width: 50px;
		height: 3px;
		background: var(--gold);
		margin: 0 auto 2rem;
		border-radius: 2px;
	}

	/* ═══════════════════════════════════════
	   SLIDE 4 — TIMELINE (light)
	   ═══════════════════════════════════════ */
	.slide-parcours {
		background: var(--light);
	}

	.slide-parcours h2 {
		text-align: center;
		font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.75rem);
		color: var(--blue);
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
		line-height: 1.2;
	}

	.timeline {
		position: relative;
		padding-left: 3.5rem;
	}

	.timeline::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		left: 0.5625rem;
		top: 0.375rem;
		bottom: 0.375rem;
		width: 2px;
		background: var(--border);
	}

	.tl-item {
		position: relative;
		padding-bottom: 1.75rem;
	}

	.tl-item:last-child { padding-bottom: 0; }

	.tl-item::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		left: -3.5rem;
		top: 0.375rem;
		width: 13px;
		height: 13px;
		border-radius: 50%;
		background: var(--white);
		border: 3px solid var(--border);
		transform: translateX(calc(0.5625rem - 50% + 1px));
		z-index: 1;
	}

	.tl-item.current::before {
		background: var(--red);
		border-color: var(--red);
		box-shadow: 0 0 0 5px rgba(237, 41, 57, 0.15);
	}

	.tl-year {
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: var(--blue);
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.06em;
		margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
	}

	.tl-content h4 {
		font-size: 1rem;
		color: var(--text);
		margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
		font-weight: 700;
	}

	.tl-content p {
		font-size: 0.9375rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
		color: #666;
	}

	/* ═══════════════════════════════════════
	   SLIDE 5 — EVENTS (white)
	   ═══════════════════════════════════════ */
	.slide-events {
		background: var(--white);
	}

	.slide-events h2 {
		text-align: center;
		font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.75rem);
		color: var(--blue);
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
		line-height: 1.2;
	}

	.events-placeholder {
		text-align: center;
		border: 2px dashed var(--border);
		border-radius: 12px;
		padding: 3.5rem 2rem;
		max-width: 520px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.coming-soon {
		font-size: 1.125rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: var(--blue);
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.1em;
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
	}

	.events-sub {
		font-size: 0.9375rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: #888;
		max-width: 380px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	/* ═══════════════════════════════════════
	   SLIDE 6 — CTA + FOOTER (dark navy)
	   ═══════════════════════════════════════ */
	.slide-final {
		background: var(--navy);
		color: var(--white);
		text-align: center;
	}

	.final-inner {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		justify-content: center;
		align-items: center;
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
	}

	.cta-block {
		flex: 1;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		justify-content: center;
		align-items: center;
		padding: 0 2rem;
	}

	.cta-block h2 {
		font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 3rem);
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		color: var(--white);
	}

	.cta-sub {
		font-size: 1.125rem;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.55);
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
		line-height: 1.6;
		max-width: 520px;
	}

	.cta-block .buttons {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1rem;
		justify-content: center;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
	}

	footer {
		text-align: center;
		padding: 2rem 2rem;
		font-size: 0.8125rem;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 0.75rem;
		width: 100%;
		border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
	}

	.footer-logo {
		height: 30px;
		width: auto;
		opacity: 0.3;
		filter: invert(1);
	}

	/* ═══════════════════════════════════════
	   RESPONSIVE
	   ═══════════════════════════════════════ */
	@media (max-width: 900px) {
		.priority-grid {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			max-width: 440px;
			margin: 0 auto;
		}
	}

	@media (max-width: 640px) {
		/* Relax 100vh on mobile so content doesn't overflow */
		.slide {
			min-height: 100vh;
			height: auto;
		}

		/* Hero adjustments */
		.hero-inner {
			padding: 4rem 1.5rem 3rem;
		}

		.portrait {
			width: 110px;
			height: 110px;
		}

		.slide-hero h1 {
			font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 10vw, 3.5rem);
		}

		.role {
			font-size: 1rem;
		}

		.geo {
			font-size: 0.6875rem;
			gap: 0.5rem;
		}

		.slide-hero .quote {
			font-size: 0.9375rem;
		}

		.facts {
			flex-direction: column;
			align-items: center;
			gap: 0.25rem;
		}

		.facts li {
			font-size: 0.75rem;
		}

		.cta {
			font-size: 0.9375rem;
			padding: 0.8rem 1.75rem;
			width: 100%;
			text-align: center;
		}

		.slide-hero .buttons,
		.cta-block .buttons {
			flex-direction: column;
			align-items: center;
			width: 100%;
			max-width: 320px;
		}

		/* Priorities adjustments */
		.slide-priorities h2,
		.slide-parcours h2,
		.slide-events h2 {
			margin-bottom: 2rem;
		}

		.priority-card {
			padding: 1.75rem 1.25rem;
		}

		/* Quote adjustments */
		.slide-quote blockquote {
			font-size: clamp(1.0625rem, 4vw, 1.5rem);
			padding: 0 1.5rem;
		}

		/* Timeline adjustments */
		.timeline {
			padding-left: 2.75rem;
		}

		.tl-item::before {
			left: -2.75rem;
		}

		.tl-item {
			padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
		}

		.tl-content p {
			font-size: 0.875rem;
		}

		/* Final slide */
